<p style="text-align: left;">On Rails is a newly formed post-krautrock three piece bringing together the talents of Cassette Electrik&#8217;s Oli Freke and guitarists Patrick and The Cobra. The band is currently making waves (quite literally) in the math-pop genre and their first track, Sine Language, was recorded with Geek Pop specifically in mind.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Sine Language explores natural tunings and harmonics by cycling seven sine waves in varying time frames. It starts slowly as each harmonic is added and gradually the waves are cycled quicker and quicker until they play a rhythmic pattern. Then they are manipulated in pitch giving a JS Bach organ effect by the end.</p>
